		{
			"type": "action",
			"name": "Dragging Close",
			"system": {
				"actionType": {
					"value": "action"
				},
				"description": {
					"value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> the chained soul's most recent action is a successful chain Strike</p><hr /><p>The chained soul wraps its chains around the creature's body, dragging them close in an attempt to Strike them with a slam. Trget creature must attempt at a @Check[fortitude|dc:14] save.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> the creature breaks free and insytead drags the chained souls towards them, making it falling @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.j91X7x0XSomq8d60]{Prone}.</p><p><strong>Success</strong> the creature breaks free from the chains</p><p><strong>Failure</strong> the creature is dragged by 5 feet towards the chained soul. If the creature is at reach, the chained soul attempts a slam Strike, applying the multiple attack penalty as normal.</p><p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> as failure but the creature is dragged by 10 feet towards the chained soul.</p>",
					"gm": ""
				},
